creator: MTransit Apps
descriptionHtml:
This application adds Hamilton HSR buses information to MonTransit.

This app provides the buses schedule (offline) as well as service alerts from @HSRNow and news from @HSR on Twitter.

HSR buses serve Hamilton in Ontario, Canada.

Once this application is installed, the MonTransit app will display buses information (schedule...).

This application only has a temporary icon: download the MonTransit app (free) in the "More ..." section bellow or by following this Google Play link http://goo.gl/pCk5mV

You can install this application on the SD card but it is not recommended.

The information comes from the GTFS file provided by City of Hamilton and Hamilton Street Railway.
https://www.hamilton.ca/city-initiatives/strategies-actions/open-data-program

This application is free and open-source:
https://github.com/mtransitapps/ca-hamilton-hsr-bus-android

This app is not related with City of Hamilton and Hamilton Street Railway.

Permissions:
- Other: required for real-time information and to read news from Twitter
descriptionShort: Hamilton HSR buses for MonTransit. Schedule. News. Alerts.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Schedule from March 22, 2020 to June 27, 2020.
Tweets from @HSR and @HSRNow.

title: Hamilton HSR Bus - MonTransit

creator: MTransit Apps
descriptionHtml:
This application adds Hamilton HSR buses information to MonTransit.

This app provides the buses schedule (offline) as well as service alerts from @HSRNow and news from @HSR on Twitter.

HSR buses serve Hamilton in Ontario, Canada.

Once this application is installed, the MonTransit app will display buses information (schedule...).

This application only has a temporary icon: download the MonTransit app (free) in the "More ..." section bellow or by following this Google Play link http://goo.gl/pCk5mV

You can install this application on the SD card but it is not recommended.

The information comes from the GTFS file provided by City of Hamilton and Hamilton Street Railway.
https://www.hamilton.ca/city-initiatives/strategies-actions/open-data-program

This application is free and open-source:
https://github.com/mtransitapps/ca-hamilton-hsr-bus-android

This app is not related with City of Hamilton and Hamilton Street Railway.

Permissions:
- Other: required for real-time information and to read news from Twitter
